==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unwit
<hw>Un*wit"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> not +
<ets>wit</ets>.]</ety> <def>Want of wit or understanding;
